    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, preserved in concours-level condition. This example is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS high-pressure stepless variable valve timing system for optimized volumetric efficiency across the rev range. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a limited-slip M-Variable Lock differential. The chassis exhibits factory-spec rigidity with no signs of subframe fatigue, while the suspension retains its original geometry and damping characteristics. Every mechanical component, from the rod bearings to the cooling system, has been maintained to exacting standards. A turn-key masterpiece for the purist who demands mechanical perfection and aesthetic flawlessness.",
